541
00:49:10.735 --> 00:49:12.202
That's crazy.

542
00:49:12.937 --> 00:49:15.304
He got the mole in the same place.

543
00:49:16.542 --> 00:49:21.138
No. It's not my Uncle Ferdinand.
because Uncle Ferdinand was killed by

544
